SUBLIME TEXT SETUP
==================

- Install Package Control from https://sublime.wbond.net/installation:

    import urllib.request,os,hashlib; h = '7183a2d3e96f11eeadd761d777e62404e330c659d4bb41d3bdf022e94cab3cd0'; pf = 'Package Control.sublime-package'; ipp = sublime.installed_packages_path(); urllib.request.install_opener( urllib.request.build_opener( urllib.request.ProxyHandler()) ); by = urllib.request.urlopen( 'http://sublime.wbond.net/' + pf.replace(' ', '%20')).read(); dh = hashlib.sha256(by).hexdigest(); print('Error validating download (got %s instead of %s), please try manual install' % (dh, h)) if dh != h else open(os.path.join( ipp, pf), 'wb' ).write(by)

- Install themes and plugins using Package Control (Cmd + Shift + P - Install Package):
    - Soda theme.
    - Schemr.
    - Monokai Gray & Tomorrow color schemes.

- Configure binary for term use:
    ln -s "/Applications/Sublime Text 3.app/Contents/SharedSupport/bin/subl" ~/bin/subl

- Link .dotfiles prefs file with actual Sublime Text Preferences file:
    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/sublime-text-3/Preferences.sublime-settings ~/Library/Application\ Support/Sublime\ Text\ 3/Packages/User/

